.Pp
.Fn tls_config_set_ocsp_staple_file
sets a DER-encoded OCSP response to be stapled during the TLS handshake from
the specified file.
.Pp
.Fn tls_config_set_ocsp_staple_mem
sets a DER-encoded OCSP response to be stapled during the TLS handshake from
memory.
